SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c01548422
Version: 1

HPSBMA02369 SSRT080115 rev.1 - HP ProLiant Essentials Rapid Deployment Pack (RDP) Running Symantec Altiris Deployment Solution, Remote SQL Injection, Remote or Local Gain Extended Privileges, Local Denial of Service (DoS)

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as soon as possible.

Release Date: 2008-09-17
Last Updated: 2008-09-17

Potential Security Impact: Remote SQL injection, remote gain extended privileges, local gain extended privileges, local Denial of Service (DoS)

Source: Hewlett-Packard Company, HP Software Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
Potential vulnerabilities have been identified with HP ProLiant Essentials Rapid Deployment Pack (RDP) running Symantec Altiris Deployment Solution. The vulnerabilities could be exploited remotely to perform SQL injection or to gain extended privileges. The vulnerabilities could be exploited locally to gain extended privileges or to cause a Denial of Service (DoS).

References: CVE-2008-2286, CVE-2008-2287, CVE-2008-2288, CVE-2008-2289, CVE-2008-2290, CVE-2008-2291

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.
HP ProLiant Essentials Rapid Deployment Pack (RDP) running Symantec Altiris Deployment Solution prior to v6.9.176.

BACKGROUND

CVSS 2.0 Base Metrics 
===============================================
Reference                         Base Vector               Base Score 
CVE-2008-2286     (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:P/I:P/A:P)    7.5
CVE-2008-2287     (AV:L/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)    7.2
CVE-2008-2288     (AV:L/AC:L/Au:N/C:N/I:P/A:P)     3.6
CVE-2008-2289     (AV:L/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)     7.2
CVE-2008-2290     (AV:L/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)     7.2
CVE-2008-2291     (AV:N/AC:L/Au:N/C:P/I:P/A:P)     7.5
===============================================
Information on CVSS is documented in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002.

RESOLUTION

Symantec has made an update available to resolve the vulnerabilities. To download the update go to https://kb.altiris.com and search for KB 41418. The article gives instructions for downloading and installing the update. 

PRODUCT SPECIFIC INFORMATION 
None 

